{"tid":1635804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CCTVB配合林鄭分化市民：開始叫裝修手足做\"黑衣人\", \"蒙面人\"而唔叫\"示威者\"","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:13:00.000Z","uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32505b317d618e3855b6823c24519e96205edc44","tid":1635804,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"以前咩都叫示威者, 林奠叫完你地割席之後就改晒口<br />\n黑衣人, 蒙面人, 著黑衫既人, 戴口罩既人<br />\n企圖分化和理非同勇武<br />\n<br />\n我知你地實會話冇人睇cctvb, 我都唔想睇, 無奈屋企人堅持要睇我又焗住睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋好多中立師奶廢老仲會睇, 當俾大家知道多個分化手段, 諗定點防範都好<br />\n<br />\n總之唔睇CCTVB既大家記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和勇一體, 核爆不割</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb925e858446ef8996253aaa3547eb6281701f25","tid":1635804,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ae68b78bddce00a8572cb7eb16b0ab1a6dcf5b","tid":1635804,"uid":325398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"改左稱呼都冇用，手足依然都係果班手足"},{"pid":"eeec0931bc5104a7d0c2d31e8f284597a5a34019","tid":1635804,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"同你屋企人講，全部都係臥底做既，所以淨叫黑衣人"},{"pid":"cee44bb3fe69d899c7c8aacd9d291d6c292eca48","tid":1635804,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"手足"}]}